Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.91,0:01:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇少女中的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堀江！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么的脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我把你毁掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请留意兔子的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被它绊到您如疾风般飞快的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊  可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇…水晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇少女一共有七位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在姐妹中有一位从来没有遇到过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的姐妹们都曾经在同一个时代中醒来过  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有她不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人知道的第七人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是蔷薇水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到她  是我们所有的姐妹都苏醒了的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父亲大人「爱丽丝游戏进入了最后  让爱丽丝诞生吧」的讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你不想战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,象先生一号出发咯～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:05:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗷～象先生  象先生  嗷～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到那个喷壶就令人火大的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是这么破的大象造型…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太令人不快了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  早饭做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～来了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏要抹果酱吃哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  你又来啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是好好从前门进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不要再罗嗦这么多了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真红呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚去叫过她了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在睡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见呢  是昨天晚上熬夜了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会知道这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来最近她都看书看到很晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果酱果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在看什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习的时候不要松懈的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果到最后真红还是没有下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管她的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏要用象先生给花儿浇水～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,象先生～象先生～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下的说！出大事了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红起不来可能是雏莓的原因的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是惹她生气了的说啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是的说！真红真的生气了的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会把自己关在箱子里不和任何人说话的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  怒火积攒到顶点的时候就会大爆发的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吼——！雏莓！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小雏  雏  雏…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可怕的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来确认一下的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在睡觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  进去的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出事了的说！糟糕了的说！惨了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是小雏和真红的储物架哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好看看的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小背包的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了分界线了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红就是为了这个而生气的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好  虽然我好心把地方借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不准越过这条线哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是我的架子！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就糟糕了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪会把真红惹怒了的说～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘的说  嘘的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:07:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去给我泡一杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在下面喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵  遵命哦——！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红  出什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起喝杯茶如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是像以前一样是个奇怪的孩子的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  今天的事我希望你能为我保密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.14,0:08:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为如果知道了第七人出现了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们会不知如何是好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  第七人的事不可能写在这上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况我根本看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不必客气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  今天已经说好了要回家吃饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶今天身体状况比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要亲自作饭的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…不知道怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红——！翠星石和苍星石要回去了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  你不睡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰到你了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也  也不是这样啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰到你了的话  我到下面去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七人的事告诉她们比较好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是姐妹吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算告诉她们  也只能增加些无谓的不安而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就再装得没事一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家已经在担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  雏莓  翠星石还有苍星石都是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论早晚都一个人躲在屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎一句话都不说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样当然不管是谁都会感到奇怪吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  她们问我「真红出了什么事吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事放到一边不要管就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你觉得可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你周围的人们的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被你这么说！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的事都处理不好  还对我说这种话？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我怎么样没有关系吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又想这样逃避问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有逃避！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在逃避吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  让人这么担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…搞不明白啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的生气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啊  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是生气生得很厉害的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏已经把越过线的部分放回去了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了的说～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样还不足以平息她的愤怒的说～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨碍睡眠可是连姐妹也不可原谅的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并没有睡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被赶出来了  噗～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小不点莓是味增渣的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个味增的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  翠星石和雏莓一起被赶出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也是味增渣哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的说～才怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭什么我翠星石要和你一样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石  你想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你做的事很不像你自己的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是会给纯带来麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯现在为了第二学期能够上学去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在拼命的想要赶上落下的学业
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候让他担心  实在不像是你会做出的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你像你现在的主人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有多大的烦恼都一定不会说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个麻烦的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退一百步  如果是和纯两个人之间的问题的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就什么都不管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  如果是和爱丽丝游戏有关的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝游戏是我们所有人的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是所有蔷薇少女共同的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个地方想去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能陪我一起去？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我也是最近才知道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槐老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.68,0:16:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  原来是柏叶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以打扰一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们到5点时就要关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:16:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果你不在意的话当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这一位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通朋友而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是手制的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是里面的匠人制做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对人偶感兴趣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要因为是男孩子就害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是非常的高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的时候看着会觉得她们是活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是有意识的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早之前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个人来我家里买人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说「我非常喜欢人偶  对她们投入了全部感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常的爱着她们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人偶却不会有任何回报
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是安静的坐在那里」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这并不是如此徒劳的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人这么对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「人偶并非不想回报
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是不能」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论多么的想传达自己的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法到达我们的心中…是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请不要讨厌人偶  一直喜欢她们吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是太装模作样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你们两个都无话可说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过算了  随时都可以来玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就会有新的做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个做得真的很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来的真晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？纯的书包好大哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是那个软软的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啊  纯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春期的男孩子对这种书感兴趣是很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对——！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这是什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个  这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想说的话不说也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇水晶的事  我已经告诉大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都对我说「没关系」…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有大家  就一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  这样不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  纯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:20:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次让你担心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  我也总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  这次我就原谅你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力去学习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！本来就是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别随便碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是我的仆从而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么「你是仆从  别碰我」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别总随便就说这种话！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  纪  这个为什么会发出声音呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个滚筒上不是有些小小的突起吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七人竟然出现了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要见见那个妹妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  有一直这样关心着我们的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样  总是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听到没有！喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个罗嗦的仆从呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:21:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  去给我泡一杯茶来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我非要给你泡茶不可！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.56,0:22:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己想喝的话就自己去泡…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.58,0:23:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近院子里好吵闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确可以感觉到什么人出现了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.07,0:23:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是小偷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.41,0:23:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓  你去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.85,0:23:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？小雏一个人很害怕的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.17,0:23:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.10,0:23:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此吵闹  那么应该是她来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.02,0:23:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在那种地方看到了伞呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.21,0:24:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  蔷薇少女  梦见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.15,0:24:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旋律宛如梦中所见
